{"tid":381173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港是我家","createTime":"2017-08-30T17:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T09:05:13.000Z","uid":72226,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b88e7cb08afdaa388518f95a5ba80f7341462b15","tid":381173,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那人滾出香港<br />\n試想像一下 只有英文同廣東話嘅香港<br />\n係幾咁溫馨幾咁熱鬧 減少歧視<br />\n出到街唔使心裏面喺度估估下 (呢個係咪大陸人來)<br />\n亦會犯罪率下降(暴力 性騷擾 環境污染(周街屙屎尿) )<br />\n搭地鐵又唔使咁迫 <br />\n樓價又唔會咁高 <br />\n周街都少咗好多人 成個環境輕鬆左好多<br />\n唔會再有水貨客<br />\n亦能減少香港人與大陸人結婚&gt;生大陸仔<br />\n生活節奏立即可以輕鬆啲亦都減慢啲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>即使經濟可能會衰退 , 但都係值得換返來</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4d3fd54e2337ff9df6eb116cab9c39b7f9b4b10e","tid":381173,"uid":72226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:01:59.000Z","msg":"不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd38d4c3277189a81e09b4842be2157807dde0a7","tid":381173,"uid":72226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bf36ad3a819d3b59a0af6c39028b1e1f99d00f7a","tid":381173,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"34f1c4fa724a96616962cc2cd8e5f2888e575569","tid":381173,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8b3271a5e2ed3ad5de8c620daa64b7101